[{"url_token": "silencedean", "headline": "襫", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "1415866170", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "1415866170", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "害，英澳硕全世界就只有国内觉得水，看看国内外课程设置其实也能明白原因，国内课程不少都以基础课为主，甚至硕士都还有一些乱七八糟的杂课，而国外反正我去国外第一节课教授就开门见山：你们来这里读我们都把你们视为未来的精英，你们既然交了学费那么全校所有的资源都为你们所用，怎么利用好在于你们自己。再看看课程，不少内容都是站在领导或者企业的角度进行研究，实话实说国外搞学术的是真的务实，我就没见过打官腔的教授或者校领导", "like_count": 106, "author_name": "Samael Venom", "author_id": "add57097b7edce02d0da4de766035dbc", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": [{"url_token": "yi-jia-kuai", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "1414067013", "reply_comment_id": "1415866170", "reply_root_comment_id": "1415866170", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "而且我感觉老师是真的发自内心的热爱这个专业。我们有一门课有一个教授给我们发了几个视频，她说我感觉这几个视频非常有意思，虽然我没有研究这个方向，但是我看到这些视频很有意思，就分享给大家看看。我感觉我做不到这样。", "like_count": 32, "author_name": "一加快", "author_id": "22aaf14671e2f52e1ea7f3d74a34e535", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "jia-si-te-du-yi-te", "headline": "学生", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "1863046376", "reply_comment_id": "1415866170", "reply_root_comment_id": "1415866170", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "请问您是哪所大学呀？", "like_count": 2, "author_name": "艾瑞克", "author_id": "d36470233f85b2faacdecb35bc839652", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "la-mu-36-26", "headline": "当你窥见了一丝真相，从前发生的一切在你眼里都变成了有迹可循", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "10030075392", "reply_comment_id": "1415866170", "reply_root_comment_id": "1415866170", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "真让人上头，以爱大为目标", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "貌若无盐bot", "author_id": "cd441a8920d67b72ba441ed9d0173cab", "author_is_anonymous": false}]}, {"url_token": "hu-di-27", "headline": "三十而已，还是在认真生活啊", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "1288734811", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "1288734811", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "<p>我刚出来读硕士的时候也是惊了，之前本科一学期十几门课，有很多糊弄的。这边一学期三门，quiz assignment mid-term project final安排的明明白白，学的效果好很多</p>", "like_count": 63, "author_name": "芝麻", "author_id": "a0a7afb3087cb6400d3eabd755f75c87", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": [{"url_token": "yi-jia-kuai", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "1288781453", "reply_comment_id": "1288734811", "reply_root_comment_id": "1288734811", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "而且我感觉各个课的衔接性也特别好。我们第一学期前三周学的introduction，就是很浅的专业介绍课。当时讲了一个位错概念，后来的一门课用到位错的概念，老师就说这个在前面的课讲过了，如果不清楚可以去看introduction讲义的第几章，连第几章都有了，课程设置的挺科学的。相反我国内上本科，好多时候专业课要用到基础课的东西，但基础课根本没开或者没上到那，老师就得先给我们讲这部分内容。我下两届的学弟更惨，大一上学期就上材料力学，大一下学期才有大学物理，老师又当力学老师又当物理老师，课程安排很混乱。老师当时上课就骂教务处[大笑]", "like_count": 28, "author_name": "一加快", "author_id": "22aaf14671e2f52e1ea7f3d74a34e535", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "henry-80-13", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "1508626714", "reply_comment_id": "1506257910", "reply_root_comment_id": "1288734811", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "哦噢我明白你的意思了，确实。我出国也有这种感觉，很多advanced的课也是从头开始讲，不会直接引入没介绍过的概念。", "like_count": 4, "author_name": "Henry", "author_id": "7e2f089fc8481bb1406b568258974f6a", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "christianmax", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "1572106483", "reply_comment_id": "1288734811", "reply_root_comment_id": "1288734811", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "我现在在港中深读本科也是这样的感觉[思考]", "like_count": 1, "author_name": "Christianmax", "author_id": "848e4c1a73e1dc797d209b9d1bc9437c", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "henry-80-13", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "1303048833", "reply_comment_id": "1288734811", "reply_root_comment_id": "1288734811", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "c