": " 相当赞同。我在国内读了三年。确切说是三年半。一年把课程学完，后面就是搞论文。但是学校也不怎么管。就那一年的课程也是水的不行。上专业课老师经常让学生上去讲课，分章让不同学生讲课，美其名曰提高学生自主学习能力。。。。 完全没学到什么，也没得到什么提高。就这样水水的课程，我们要出去实习也不愿意，后来我还跑到国外去实习工作，结果突然有个预答辩，没回国，导致我延期毕业了半年，我导师还想让我再荒废半年，让我延期一年。。。。关键是什么也学不到 ", "like_count": 23, "author_name": "前行的骡子", "author_id": "670c0fade38f2ec129215fb039f8ff0a", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": []}, {"url_token": "wanghanyu-95", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "2310615999", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "2310615999", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "国内研究生老师把学生当廉价劳动力的，大有人在。", "like_count": 6, "author_name": "wanghanyu", "author_id": "215786de7e9f174155fbf2c951727072", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": []}, {"url_token": "mint-96-28", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "2198686431", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "2198686431", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "其实海外（尤其是欧洲英美岗）授课型硕士真的很实用很硬核，但国内硕的人总是觉得我们水。🙂🙂🙂🙂", "like_count": 6, "author_name": "朝朝夕夕迟", "author_id": "ab3d2d37926dd97b34a86aed7997795d", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": []}, {"url_token": "hou-jia-cheng-86", "headline": "a slow learner", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "1902075813", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "1902075813", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "对，好多人还以为授课型读不了博[笑哭]，不过英国博士奖学金是真的不好拿，自费真的很多人难以负担[捂脸]", "like_count": 2, "author_name": "Hjc2016s", "author_id": "87bb5b63def11d30ff6bde2679b943de", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": []}, {"url_token": "bi-ba-bu-ou-12", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "1543486506", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "1543486506", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "笔者好！请问博士是自费吗", "like_count": 1, "author_name": "比巴卜欧", "author_id": "7f304b6b1e73cbdfbecb6af920ccc4c0", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": []}, {"url_token": "sql-55", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "1302810035", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "1302810035", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "笔者好！我今年也即将上港校一年制硕士，怎么申请本校博士啊，跪求了！", "like_count": 1, "author_name": "SQL", "author_id": "4979376cae7c5be3d8de2e053ddcffec", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": [{"url_token": "yi-jia-kuai", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "1303405575", "reply_comment_id": "1302810035", "reply_root_comment_id": "1302810035", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "就跟老师发邮件表明自己的意向，cv发给老师，本校的学生老师更愿意回复的，而且成功几率更高", "like_count": 5, "author_name": "一加快", "author_id": "22aaf14671e2f52e1ea7f3d74a34e535", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "li-mu-99-46-99", "headline": "中了代表的毒，症状已持续半年", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "1447336256", "reply_comment_id": "1302810035", "reply_root_comment_id": "1302810035", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "这种曲线申phd的方式很常见，因为你在这学校的一年有直接的机会面对面接触目标教授，利用这一年时间跟他做科研，如果表现好有一定概率能留你读phd。但是事先一定要搞清楚目标教授是否有招收的预算，最好一开始就表明自己想读phd的意愿，目的一定要明确", "like_count": 1, "author_name": "S画廊理事", "author_id": "98229383efa8fd9151a9c72b9a576d39", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "sql-55", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "1839466297", "reply_comment_id": "1654996809", "reply_root_comment_id": "1302810035", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "谢谢你！很感谢 🙏", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "SQL", "author_id": "4979376cae7c5be3d8de2e053ddcffec", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "dong-pin-xi-cou-52", "headline": "拆东墙补西墙。拆西墙补南墙", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "1654996809", "reply_comment_id": "1302810035", "reply_root_comment_id": "1302810035", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "现在就开始搜学校网站，然后看到教授研究方向契合直接发邮件联系，说自己是本校的硕士，对他的研究很感兴趣，有的教授会让你和他面谈，或者直接进他的组里体验。我在香港的时候碰到的教授都很乐意学生去找他们。", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "东拼西凑", "author_id": "f14e18c0de42e867fe55d1becb2a72d7", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "sql-55", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "1447156589", "reply_comment_id": "1447336256", "reply_root_comment_id": "1302810035", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "谢谢🙏！", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "SQL", "author_id": "4979376cae7c5be3d8de2e053ddcffec", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "yi-jia-kuai", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "1302540990", "reply_comment_id": "1302810035", "reply_root_comment_id": "1302810035", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "费用支出你可以看看学校官网，我有两个论文，但是是中文的，不是很好的文章。有国家奖学金", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "一加快", "author_id": "22aaf14671e2f52e1ea7f3d74a34e535", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "sql-55", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "1302362249", "reply_comment_id": "1303405575", "reply_root_comment_id": "1302810035", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "噢噢！那个人简历这块，可不可以请问下你有什么优势吗，比如说有没有科研经历。另外，读博学费会很高吗", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "SQL", "author_id": "4979376cae7c5be3d8de2e053ddcffec", "author_is_anonymous": false}]}]